    },
    {
      "text": "Rockin' Pretty, known in Japan and South Korea as Happy Star Band (ハッピー☆スター☆バンド, Happī☆Sutā☆Bando) (Korean: 해피 스타 밴드 ~전국민 오디션 밴드편~) and in Europe as Diva Girls: Making the Music, is a 2009 rhythm game. It was developed and published in Japan by Arc System Works, in Europe by 505 Games, in North America by Aksys Games, and in South Korea by CyberFront Korea.",
